* Daniel Garber, landscape painter, instructor at the Pennsylvania Academy of the Fine Arts
* L. Birge Harrison, landscape painter, instructor at the Art Students League of New York
* John Fulton Folinsbee, landscape and marine painter
* William Langson Lathrop, landscape painter, founder of the New Hope art colony
